Package: GCSignatureFramework
Title: Modernized Biomarker Discovery Framework for the 12-Gene Gastric Cancer Signature
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Nhan", "Tran", email = "nhan.tran@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Repository for Part 2 of the 12-Gene Gastric Cancer Signature
    project: a Modernized Biomarker Discovery Framework benchmarking
    contemporary machine learning methodology (LASSO, Elastic Net,
    Bootstrap validation, Nested CV, Stability selection) against the
    classical statistical reconstruction completed in Part 1. This
    package is bootstrapped under Module 01 — Repository Bootstrap and
    is built out incrementally under the locked governance chain
    (FRAMEWORK_SPEC, IDS-001 through IDS-006, MODULE_TAXONOMY,
    IMPLEMENTATION_MASTER_PLAN, CODING_PHASE_PHILOSOPHY).
